和系列其他作品一样，《勇者斗恶龙V》在日本非常畅销。超级任天堂版在日本售出了280万份，PlayStation 2重制版售出了164万份<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.the-magicbox.com/Chart-JPPlatinum.shtml |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-01-14 |archive-date=2012-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017061224/http://the-magicbox.com/Chart-JPPlatinum.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2006年日本游戏杂志《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》举办的读者百佳游戏票选中，原版游戏排到了第11位，PS2重制版排到了第40位<ref>{{cite web | author=Colin Campbell | title=Japan Votes on All Time Top 100 | url=http://www.next-gen.biz/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100 | work=''[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]'' | date=2006-03-03 | accessdate=2011-02-24 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080723051728/http://www.edge-online.com/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100 | archivedate=2008-07-23 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>。将游戏故事被分成不同的时间段一直受到赞扬，當時只有为数不多的电子游戏会使用此手法<ref name="hg">{{cite web | author=Kurt Kalata | year=2007 |title=Dragon Quest V | url=http://hardcoregaming101.net/dragonquest/dragonquest.htm | work= | accessdate=2008-01-29}}</ref><ref name="boz" /><ref name="kurt">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/3520/the_history_of_dragon_quest.php|title=The History of Dragon Quest|first=Kurt|last=Kalata|publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|work=Features|page=1|accessdate=2009-09-20|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520113408/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/3520/the_history_of_dragon_quest.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏的处理[[教育小说|成长]]主题的方式也受到稱道，[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]评价“从没游戏能像《勇者斗恶龙V》一样将其做到如此壯麗”<ref>Kurt Kalata, [http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/3581/a_japanese_rpg_primer_the_.php?page=13 A Japanese RPG Primer: The Essential 20 - Dragon Quest V], [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]</ref>。游戏也被认为是堀井雄二在系列中最喜欢的作品<ref name="hg" />。

2008年发售的任天堂DS重制版是該年日本第七畅销的游戏，在日本賣出了117萬份<ref name="famitsu2008">{{cite web |title=JAPANESE 2008 MARKET REPORT |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090402121525/https://www.mcvuk.com/features/403/JAPANESE-2008-MARKET-REPORT|publisher=[[MCVUK|MCVUK]] |accessdate=2009-01-09}}</ref>，後在2009年達到全球累計135万份的銷量<ref>{{cite web | title=Results Briefing: Fiscal Year ended May 31, 2009 | date=2009-05-19 | url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716123012/http://www.square-enix.com/eng/pdf/news/20090525_01en.pdf| work=Square-Enix.com | accessdate=2009-07-21}}</ref>。有評論认为游戏是DS上最好的RPG之一，也是“该平台上情节最佳的游戏之一”<ref name="boz" /><ref name="edey">{{cite web | author=Edey, Brian | title=Review: Dragon Quest V | date=2009-03-16 | url=http://www.gamefocus.ca/?nav=reviewCard&fid=8590 | work=Gamefocus.com.com | accessdate=2009-10-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100723012506/http://www.gamefocus.ca/?nav=reviewCard&fid=8590 | archive-date=2010-07-23 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。虽然有批评认为游戏的界面过于陈旧和简单，但亦有评论认为游戏感人的情节盖过了其缺陷，评论还称“这是最伟大的传统RPG之一”<ref name="chad">{{cite web | author=Chadwell, Dustin | date=2009-03-25 | title=Dragon Quest V | url=http://www.gaming-age.com/cgi-bin/reviews/review.pl?sys=nds&game=dqv | work=gaming-age.com | accessdate=2009-09-30 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://archive.is/20091003233551/http://www.gaming-age.com/cgi-bin/reviews/review.pl?sys=nds&game=dqv | archivedate=2009-10-03 }}</ref>。<!-- Other critics note that this installment of the series particularly stands out from the rest because of its story telling, differentiating it from other ''Dragon Quest'' games, which are all more similar.<ref name="chad" /> [[1UP.com|1UP]] praised it for its mature storytelling that "gets better with age" and resonates with players with a "more mature and experienced" perspective going through similar phases in their own life.<ref>Jeremy Parish, [http://www.1up.com/do/blogEntry?bId=8983724&publicUserId=5379721 Dragon Quest V and the Maturation of Perspective] {{Wayback|url=http://www.1up.com/do/blogEntry?bId=8983724&publicUserId=5379721 |date=20160304235710 }}, [[1UP.com|1UP]], March 16, 2009</ref> The updated 3D environments with rotable camera have also received praise.<ref name="edey" /> -->

